rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1w-bp620g-351\"><a><u>Candra Ricky Susanto, Vincent Debast</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l1w-k9ooud-352\"><a id=\"_x5gzec6f0lg\" display=\"false\"></a><strong>Related Documents</strong></h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1w-e7bqjs-353\"><strong>Document name</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1x-9vtu9j-354\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1x-i97usu-355\"><strong>Link to document</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1x-p3ptha-356\">Withdrawal Account Creation Request</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1x-xxfr5t-357\">Initial document (2021) to kick off withdrawal bank account collection practice</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1x-w41hqz-358\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1aFHqvkiTPFf9zis7gpTV1mqL5iQnhMGhjoPZW2wz6B0/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.gzrbdpkp4l0i\"><u>[SOP] Withdrawal Account manual creation</u></a></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-rueg04-359\"><a id=\"_x8qwt25al81j\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-d5mtto-360\"><a id=\"_hgv8mbgs0teg\" display=\"false\"></a><strong>Merchant Requirements</strong> </h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:566px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-hph901-361\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-vxxu93-362\"><strong>Requirement</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"566\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-nro5sv-363\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1y-f6n9oa-364\">Bank Book </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-kfil6u-365\"><strong>For Entity:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-vqx5v0-366\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-p73bob-367\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-eqg8j3-795\">Bank Account Name = Legal Entities’ Name --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-468svm-368\"><strong>For CV (ID)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-2knll1-369\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-j16qv4-370\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-jr3xbs-796\">One of:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-9rvsx5-371\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-j9cq5h-372\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-lboku1-797\">Bank Account Name = Legal Entities’ Name --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-glh6w9-373\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-hqawci-798\">Bank Account Name = Name of Business Owner --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong> </p></li></ul></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-fpll2e-374\"><strong>Sole Proprietorship:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-6npzg8-375\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-g1fs3i-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-h7lz6p-799\">Bank Account Name = Legal Entities’ Name --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-m09lmn-377\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-jvffuk-800\">Bank Account Name = Name of Business Owner* --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-i50d0c-378\"><strong>Individual:</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-aymzin-379\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-swyjlm-380\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx7-75ghpi-801\">Bank Account Name = Name of Business Owner --&gt; <strong><em>approved</em></strong></p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l1z-jfnzxi-381\"><em>*Only applicable to </em><strong><em>non-Indonesian Sole Proprietorship</em></strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"566\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-0dcydr-382\">Bank books display bank account number, bank account name and bank name.</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-xyk5cf-383\">Statement letter and Buku Nikah / Kartu Keluarga (Tentative)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-izuwwn-384\"><em>*This only applicable for Individual merchants who want to add spouse bank account</em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-b0ymhs-385\">Merchants need submit signed letter with duty stamp (materai) and copy of Buku Nikah / Kartu Keluarga</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"566\"><ol data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-4n9do5-386\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l20-8pn9j3-387\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx8-ljs1l5-802\">Template for Surat Penunjukan Using Family Name:<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RcoR4rNjtfC9knrFrpYKp3pXD_rae1GoLfSqalQUUrA/edit?tab=t.0\"><u>Template Surat Penunjukan Rekening Berbeda - Using Other Family Name</u></a></p></li></ol></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-evorpz-388\">Virtual account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-v5w40b-389\">A letter from the VA provider on official letterhead, confirming that the virtual account belongs to the merchant and including the merchant’s entity registration number.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"566\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-y19fnl-390\">Merchants may sometimes request to only provide a screenshot of the provider’s page (e.g. Wise, Aspire, etc.).Screenshots are not sufficient. An official letter from the VA provider remains mandatory, as this is a Compliance requirement.</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-bbkcg5-391\">For PT/PP/CV/Yayasan etc - ideally they need to submit bank account withdrawal under their legal name. but in cases where they don’t have company’s bank account, next step can either: use Surat Penunjukan Sementara and must submit the right bank account (match with legal name) within 2 weeks or use Surat Penunjukan Permanen</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd95mk7-i87lsb-573\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-eulp2h-394\">p.s: Both letter can use by anyone, doesn’t need to be directors, but need sign and approval from their director and they need attach KTP of the person appointed. And please also use letterhead in Surat Penunjukan to formalize.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-yxsvf0-397\">For :</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-kzs9tn-398\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-fnkfdu-399\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-y8mc1n-803\">Individual - ideally under director’s name, but if director doesn’t have bank account, we can accept only family member, and beside surat Penunjukan, please ask for KTP + KK</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l21-b5cvtg-400\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-b1s2uz-804\">Sole Prop in ID - Now we can add a bank account under the director's name.</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"566\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-djohpf-401\">This is for format template:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-fxlniu-402\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-f3y476-403\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-xzuh0f-805\">Surat Penunjukan <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1dpSn6DTklfsUjxCHjZ4KtH8Suyg3tPxmYOe3MlCtJ0k/edit?tab=t.0\">Sementara</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-jptei1-404\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-qq2bhw-806\">Surat Penunjukan <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Fz1Tg7ZaerWrkYijxqs_dB6av6wNV97b/edit\">Permanen</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-yyggez-405\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-pe8uwb-807\">Surat Penunjukan <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RcoR4rNjtfC9knrFrpYKp3pXD_rae1GoLfSqalQUUrA/edit?tab=t.0\">Family Member</a></p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-lk5rpy-406\"><a id=\"_g13bwb7nnnfa\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-9wqkoo-407\"><a id=\"_avxt42xdqagy\" display=\"false\"></a><strong>SLA</strong><br type=\"inline\"></h2><h4 data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-9wqkoo-407\">MO:</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-lefz32-410\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-ushcmc-411\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjx9-ieu473-808\">Approval bank account - Same Working Day, if we receive complete documents and data matched</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-1nlokv-412\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd9oftl-b892jp-580\">Feedback -  Same Working Day</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-twyfow-415\"><a id=\"_z61wcoo1lcez\" display=\"false\"></a><strong>Country Rules</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l22-fzlerj-416\">Indonesia 🇮🇩</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l23-xvht1c-417\"><strong>Country</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l23-42j947-418\"><strong>Bank Account Name</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l23-fa7hcs-419\">Entity Bank Account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l23-utkyfw-420\">Director Bank Account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l23-927xu8-421\">PT / Yayasan</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l24-znmgzn-422\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l24-58rbu0-423\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l24-5tpz57-424\">CV</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l24-nqdxer-425\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l24-23c5u2-426\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l25-h7i7ir-427\">Sole Proprietor</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l25-kazow1-428\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l25-jqa1bb-429\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l25-f130t6-430\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l25-fprfwb-431\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-enerm5-432\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-8wbua0-433\">Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-xyqynn-434\">❌</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-fbwp9n-435\">✅</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-jn7vkv-436\">Philippines 🇵🇭</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l26-e1d60f-437\"><strong>Country</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-v6rx8g-438\"><strong>Bank Account Name</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-959fag-439\">Entity Bank Account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-phq2p2-440\">Director Bank Account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-pf6n01-441\">Corporation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-vv5pt8-442\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l27-iwayds-443\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l28-xrr67w-444\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l28-qqx1a3-445\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l28-dxuhzz-446\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l28-9p8qm9-447\">Sole Proprietor</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l28-x0dyns-448\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-x9zz02-449\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-rj700f-450\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-we4ipr-451\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-hx5gb2-452\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-up8r7u-453\">Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l29-b746fg-454\">❌</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-tdp2io-455\">✅</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-ovbdy2-456\"><em>(Due to limitations in account information visibility, bank account verification via bank applications is not supported in the PH).</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-t9l4lf-457\">Malaysia 🇲🇾</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-lh5sjm-458\"><strong>Country</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-tfacb6-459\"><strong>Bank Account Name</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-q9lhsn-460\">Entity Bank Account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2a-e2ty29-461\">Director Bank Account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-epncce-462\">Private Limited Company</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-qfmoyv-463\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-0gp6rt-464\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-5ls7oe-465\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-ece5h8-466\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2b-a9z97s-467\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-4v9lmw-468\">Sole Proprietor</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-rmjboi-469\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-mfvh6r-470\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-hlai4p-471\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-a4enld-472\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-e41wwr-473\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2c-877vjs-474\">Thailand 🇹🇭</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-svmecz-475\"><strong>Country</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-prspu6-476\"><strong>Bank Account Name</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-h98evi-477\">Entity Bank Account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-oakv2n-478\">Director Bank Account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-7y470e-479\">Thai Limited Company / Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2d-skuirq-480\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-fehsn6-481\">✅</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-vwz7jp-482\">(Need copy of the board resolution)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-9fuoqc-483\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-1c7hsr-484\">✅</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-ksbht5-485\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-d9wtqa-486\"><a id=\"_qkw0q9zb1qje\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-oavowv-487\"><a id=\"_c30emfink90x\" display=\"false\"></a>Process Step</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2e-d7jw2d-488\"><strong>No.</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-c92gng-489\"><strong>Process</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-qhek5s-490\"><strong>Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-jus2w7-491\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-pf9lz5-492\">Merchant request to add bank account to their dashboard</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-vwq3ht-493\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-x47e10-494\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2f-ksmb76-495\">MO check slack channel #bank-account-verif-requests</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-6504if-496\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-81k7re-497\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-5iw2ke-498\">MO check bank account verification in #bank-account-verif-requests</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-dkaygt-499\">MO need to check : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-mgtqgb-500\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-zd4s6e-501\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxk-c9ekwq-809\">Currency</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-4rxp6e-502\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxk-abv91t-810\">Bank name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-bwcwus-503\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxk-zo6ppp-811\">Bank account number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-uvimvg-504\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxk-sc3rpf-812\">Account holder name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-8w776l-505\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxk-d7e89p-813\">Supporting docs (please check the doc attached should be the same with data in #bank-account-verif-requests)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-m57e6y-506\"><em>*in case merchant want to add another currency e.g. USD, we need to wait for SWIFT Code from Finops</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-4h0rx1-507\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-lbz96y-508\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-fb8ie84c.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2g-9tufl4-509\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-l2r1cd-510\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-hp8bzt-511\">MO opens the dashboard (Customer Management) and verify data between #bank-account-verif-requests and the dashboard.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-vyw63p-512\">For Entity check legal name (please also check their legal name in their legal document e.g. NPWP)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-2rj4eb-513\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-ks0ph8-514\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-gqy2mzry.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-7s0s9b-515\">For Individuals check  authorized signatory (please also check their name in ID Card)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-ohrfpd-516\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-urq71s-517\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-eabm8qsx.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-kjlvvw-518\"> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-zv2cj3-519\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-ux9m8j-520\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-bc5aag-521\">If all data has matched MO needs to click “approve” and if mismatched </p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-tbunft-522\">please click “reject” and choose the rejection reason</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-7283jp-523\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2h-0k8451-524\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-z6iupp7d.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-hgahg9-525\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-mfo362-526\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-oell7e7s.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-xve1fj-527\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-glgoqy-528\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-btaqu2-529\">Once the bank account is approved, the bank account will display in the dashboard and can be used by the merchant, and activation log will be displayed in #bank-account-verif-requests</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-88wjm1-530\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-0h2h1a-531\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-f5bz6ljg.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-qi5gfm-532\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-i4w8kr-533\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-5qeh51f9.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-a7nmwk-534\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2i-z59gib-535\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-bg3x5z-536\">If the bank account cannot be approved in channel #bank-account-verif-requests, MO can also add it manually in dashboard.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-05okn0-537\">Choose “add new”</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-x6vgbt-538\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-ijwxzw-539\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-amhfk3g8.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-q8hbjh-540\">Choose bank, fill account name and account number, then click “add”</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-40f0xf-541\"><img data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-ehdege-542\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-bank-account-withdrawal-image-jy6ghzeo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-i1m5cu-543\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-wjyo3c-544\"><a id=\"_59b0cemn96zs\" display=\"false\"></a></h2><h2 data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-07rh87-545\"><a id=\"_1hpxiwkrpax\" display=\"false\"></a><strong>Edge Cases</strong></h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-huk2ka-546\"><strong>No.</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-tn151n-547\"><strong>Process</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2j-y64msd-548\"><strong>Next step</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-l0is65-549\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-9afpvu-550\">Merchant want to add Spouse bank account</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-zqe4l7-551\">Base on document <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1aFHqvkiTPFf9zis7gpTV1mqL5iQnhMGhjoPZW2wz6B0/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.gzrbdpkp4l0i\"><u>[SOP] Withdrawal Account manual creation</u></a> we can add spouse bank account with additional document (Buku nikah / Kartu keluarga) and statement letter from merchant <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RcoR4rNjtfC9knrFrpYKp3pXD_rae1GoLfSqalQUUrA/edit?tab=t.0\"><u>Template Surat Penunjukan Rekening Berbeda - Using Other Family Name</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-sto4ha-552\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-5h4y6d-553\">Merchant entity want to add bank account not under PT/CV/Yayasan name</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-b04y69-554\">We can process this request, if they want to add bank account under different name for : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-pr6p2h-555\"><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-padp6r-556\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxp-x1djbw-814\"> Temporary please use <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1dpSn6DTklfsUjxCHjZ4KtH8Suyg3tPxmYOe3MlCtJ0k/edit?tab=t.0\"><u>Template Surat Penunjukan Rekening Berbeda</u></a> </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmd94l2k-srvjxc-557\"><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxp-f1qcho-815\">Permanent please use <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Fz1Tg7ZaerWrkYijxqs_dB6av6wNV97b/edit\"><u>05. Template Surat Penunjukan Rekening Berbeda - Permanent.docx</u></a></p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-ubpwq9-558\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-k5ar3s-559\">Merchant under XP Owned want to add bank account under Director / Entity name</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-kdqohi-560\">Currently for XP account we cannot process their request and bank account will follow their master account</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-klzqwh-561\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-hnmsf7-562\">ID local entity want to add bank account overseas with USD currency</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2l-wihkqp-563\">We cannot process this request, we only provide IDR withdrawal for Indonesian Entity. Ref <a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/C04BKLCTG31/p1711441662637329?thread_ts=1711429428.718709&amp;cid=C04BKLCTG31\"><u>here</u></a> </p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-j4nfmv-564\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-mp5w16-565\">Merchant ID is Entity and included in program BHP, they want add bank account under individual because they did not have bank account under entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-gv0h5u-566\">We can process this request with additional document: </p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-d1et9d-567\">- Merchant harus melampirkan surat penunjukan rekeningnya</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-12plmb-568\">- Merchant harus melampirkan KTP atas nama orang tersebut</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-agfb8t-569\">- Nama orangnya harus terlampir dan tersebut pada dokumen Akta</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-5ij1of-570\">- Merchant harus melampirkan bank booknya dengan atas nama orang tersebut</p><p data-block-id=\"mmd94l2m-6ni3c7-571\">Ref thread : https://xendit.slack.com/archives/C04BKLCTG31/p1735896808989899</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmt0pjxr-16jmg7-816\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Slug":"bank-account-withdrawal","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Slug":"bank-account-withdrawal","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Slug":"bank-account-withdrawal","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Bank Account Withdrawal","Description":null}]